  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_4_2152-2193",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2152-2193",
      "markText": "米哈依尔·戈尔巴乔夫也可以入围，因为他认识到长期的共产主义影响使苏联沦为二流国家。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2152&rangeEnd=2193",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2152&rangeEnd=2193"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_11_26270-26304",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "26270-26304",
      "markText": "中国革命没有毛，就决不会点燃起火来。没有周，它就会烧光，只剩下灰烬。",
      "totalCount": 403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=26270&rangeEnd=26304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=26270&rangeEnd=26304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_6_534-574",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "534-574",
      "markText": "他说：“我们大家都是虫子。”他接着又补充说，“不过，我的确认为我是一只萤火虫”。",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=534&rangeEnd=574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=534&rangeEnd=574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_4_833-876",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "833-876",
      "markText": "我发现写作是保持头脑活跃和敏锐的最好办法，因为只有写作和作决策一样，需要思想高度集中。",
      "totalCount": 364,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=833&rangeEnd=876",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=833&rangeEnd=876"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_5_2091-2130",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2091-2130",
      "markText": "不过，如果没有丘吉尔，西欧也许会遭到奴役；如果没有斯大林，东欧也许已获得自由。",
      "totalCount": 351,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2091&rangeEnd=2130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2091&rangeEnd=2130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_3_3033-3130",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3033-3130",
      "markText": "“美国在同世界各国相处时，最常犯的一个毛病，就是我们往往用西方民主的标准来衡量各国政府，用西欧的标准来衡量各国的文化。”“西方民主是经过几个世纪才发展起来，并扎下根的，它并不是笔直的阳关大道。”",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3033&rangeEnd=3130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3033&rangeEnd=3130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_6_6544-6612",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6544-6612",
      "markText": "第一位女议员阿斯特女士有一次对他说，“如果我是你的妻子，我会在你的咖啡里下毒”。丘吉尔反驳说，“如果我是你的丈夫，我会喝下那杯咖啡的”。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6544&rangeEnd=6612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6544&rangeEnd=6612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_11_26428-26487",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "26428-26487",
      "markText": "有着世界上最能干的十亿人民和庞大的自然资源的中国，不仅能够成为世界上人口最多的国家，而且也能够成为世界上最强大的国家。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=26428&rangeEnd=26487",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=26428&rangeEnd=26487"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_5_1771-1832",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1771-1832",
      "markText": "也有另一些人物，他们虽是大国的大人物，却生活在巨人的阴影之中：例如周恩来，他总是小心翼翼地让舞台上的聚光灯照射在毛的身上。",
      "totalCount": 308,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_6_1185-1244",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1185-1244",
      "markText": "头一天晚上，我花了一个多小时准备了一篇历时一分半钟的欢迎词。他的飞机进入视野以后，我在脑子里迅速地把欢迎词复习了一遍。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1244",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1244"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_11_6014-6073",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6014-6073",
      "markText": "“伟大来自对细节的注意。”就周而言，这句箴言几乎确实有几分道理。然而，即使他在亲自护理每一棵树木时，也总能够看到森林。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6014&rangeEnd=6073",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6014&rangeEnd=6073"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_11_7206-7259",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7206-7259",
      "markText": "事实上，中国人坚信不疑地认为，他们的文化和哲学极为优越，确信到时候就会战胜我们的和其他任何人的文化和哲学。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7206&rangeEnd=7259",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7206&rangeEnd=7259"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_11_9562-9640",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "9562-9640",
      "markText": "马克思列宁主义有一种决定论的历史观。它的信徒们相信历史必定走向世界共产主义，相信加速历史的这种进程是他们的职责。他们这样看待自己，所以就避开道德的一切考虑。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23410545&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9562&rangeEnd=9640",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b332800716537711b32349?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9562&rangeEnd=9640"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23410545_4_1438-1483",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1438-1483",
